# Zealflow CLI
A headless terminal connector for interfacing securely entirely via local configurations with your backend.

## Usage
- `zealflow configure --api-url http://localhost:8000`
- `zealflow admin create ./myschema.json`
- `zealflow admin export <form_id> --out data.csv`
- `zealflow fill <form_id>`
